<module>
    <h>bàn</h>
    <p><g>bàn</g>
        <en>white, pale, light, fair</en> is a <a href="?xx=adjectives/simple_adjectives">simple
            adjective</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-predicate">
            <h>predicate</h>
            <p><g>bàn</g> can be used as the predicate of the verb <a href="?gd=bi"
                ><g>bi</g></a>.</p>
            <p>Examples with a human subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri bheag <m>bàn</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Little Mary is fair-haired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 8</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with an animal subject – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha an cat <m>bàn</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>The cat is white.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 6</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p>Examples with more than one predicate – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Màiri <m>beag bàn</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary is small and fair-haired.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 8</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>

        </section>

        <section id="uses-mod">
            <h>modifier</h>
            <p><g>bàn</g> can be used to modify a <a href="?xx=nouns/proper_nouns">proper
                noun</a>.</p>
            <p>Some examples – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha <m>Màiri bhàn</m> anns an achadh an diugh agus tha i ag obair gu
                            trang.</gd>
                        <tr>Fair-headed Mary is in the field today and she is working busily.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
            <p><g>bàn</g> can also be used to modify a <a href="?xx=nouns/common_nouns">common
                    noun</a>.</p>
            <p>Some examples – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha an <m>cat beag bàn</m> aig an teine.</gd>
                        <tr>The little white cat is by the fire.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha falt dubh air Calum ach tha <m>falt bàn</m> air Màiri.</gd>
                        <tr>Calum has black hair but Mary has fair hair.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 9</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil <m>falt bàn</m> air Seumas?</gd>
                        <tr>Does James have fair hair?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 13–14</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Càit a bheil an <m>cat bàn</m> an diugh?</gd>
                        <tr>Where is the white cat today?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>

    </section>



</module>
